Package: stm
Title: Ecological model estimation and inference   
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c( person("Jae", "Choi", email="choijaeseok@gmail.com", role=c("aut", "cre")) ) 
Description: Ecosystem models using constrained kernel-based approximations to estimate and develop statistical inference of space-time hierarchical models. This package interacts with other em* projects.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0), 
  mvtnorm, 
  truncnorm
